#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn35.97"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.97:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.97:0.2"
msgid "10. Saḷavagga "
msgstr "10. The Sixes "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 97. Pamādavihārīsutta → pamādavihārisuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn35.97:0.3"
msgid "97. Pamādavihārīsutta "
msgstr "97. One Who Lives Negligently "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.78, sc1
msgctxt "sn35.97:1.1"
msgid "“Pamādavihāriñca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi appamādavihāriñca. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you who lives negligently and who lives diligently. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha. "
msgstr "Listen … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.97:1.3"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, pamādavihārī hoti? "
msgstr "And how does someone live negligently? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: byāsiñcati → byāsiccati (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn35.97:1.4"
msgid "Cakkhundriyaṃ asaṃvutassa, bhikkhave, viharato cittaṃ byāsiñcati cakkhuviññeyyesu rūpesu. "
msgstr "When you live with the eye faculty unrestrained, your mind becomes polluted when it comes to sights known by the eye. "

# NOTE: MS punctuates incorrectly, I have corrected.
msgctxt "sn35.97:1.5"
msgid "tassa byāsittacittassa pāmojjaṃ na hoti. "
msgstr "When the mind is polluted, there’s no joy. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.6"
msgid "Pāmojje asati pīti na hoti. "
msgstr "When there’s no joy, there’s no rapture. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.7"
msgid "Pītiyā asati passaddhi na hoti. "
msgstr "When there’s no rapture, there’s no tranquility. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.8"
msgid "Passaddhiyā asati dukkhaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "When there’s no tranquility, there’s suffering. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.9"
msgid "Dukkhino cittaṃ na samādhiyati. "
msgstr "When one is suffering, the mind does not become immersed in samādhi. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.10"
msgid "Asamāhite citte dhammā na pātubhavanti. "
msgstr "When the mind is not immersed in samādhi, principles do not become clear. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.11"
msgid "Dhammānaṃ apātubhāvā pamādavihārītveva saṅkhaṃ gacchati … pe … "
msgstr "Because principles have not become clear, you’re considered to live negligently. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.97:1.12"
msgid "jivhindriyaṃ asaṃvutassa, bhikkhave, viharato cittaṃ byāsiñcati jivhāviññeyyesu rasesu, "
msgstr "When you live with the ear … nose … tongue … body … "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.13"
msgid "tassa byāsittacittassa … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.14"
msgid "pamādavihārītveva saṅkhaṃ gacchati … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.15"
msgid "manindriyaṃ asaṃvutassa, bhikkhave, viharato cittaṃ byāsiñcati manoviññeyyesu dhammesu, "
msgstr "mind faculty unrestrained, your mind becomes polluted when it comes to thoughts known by the mind. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.16"
msgid "tassa byāsittacittassa pāmojjaṃ na hoti. "
msgstr "When the mind is polluted, there’s no joy. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.17"
msgid "Pāmojje asati pīti na hoti. "
msgstr "When there’s no joy, there’s no rapture. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.18"
msgid "Pītiyā asati passaddhi na hoti. "
msgstr "When there’s no rapture, there’s no tranquility. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.19"
msgid "Passaddhiyā asati dukkhaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "When there’s no tranquility, there’s suffering. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.20"
msgid "Dukkhino cittaṃ na samādhiyati. "
msgstr "When one is suffering, the mind does not become immersed in samādhi. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.21"
msgid "Asamāhite citte dhammā na pātubhavanti. "
msgstr "When the mind is not immersed in samādhi, principles do not become clear. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:1.22"
msgid "Dhammānaṃ apātubhāvā pamādavihārītveva saṅkhaṃ gacchati. "
msgstr "Because principles have not become clear, you’re considered to live negligently. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.97:1.23"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pamādavihārī hoti. "
msgstr "That’s how someone lives negligently. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.79, sc2
msgctxt "sn35.97:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, appamādavihārī hoti? "
msgstr "And how does someone live diligently? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.97:2.2"
msgid "Cakkhundriyaṃ saṃvutassa, bhikkhave, viharato cittaṃ na byāsiñcati cakkhuviññeyyesu rūpesu, "
msgstr "When you live with the eye faculty restrained, your mind doesn’t become polluted when it comes to sights known by the eye. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:2.3"
msgid "tassa abyāsittacittassa pāmojjaṃ jāyati. "
msgstr "When the mind isn’t polluted, joy springs up. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:2.4"
msgid "Pamuditassa pīti jāyati. "
msgstr "Being joyful, rapture springs up. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:2.5"
msgid "Pītimanassa kāyo passambhati. "
msgstr "When the mind is full of rapture, the body becomes tranquil. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:2.6"
msgid "Passaddhakāyo sukhaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "When the body is tranquil, one feels bliss. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:2.7"
msgid "Sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati. "
msgstr "And when blissful, the mind becomes immersed in samādhi. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:2.8"
msgid "Samāhite citte dhammā pātubhavanti. "
msgstr "When the mind is immersed in samādhi, principles become clear. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:2.9"
msgid "Dhammānaṃ pātubhāvā appamādavihārītveva saṅkhaṃ gacchati … pe … "
msgstr "Because principles have become clear, you’re considered to live diligently. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.97:2.10"
msgid "jivhindriyaṃ saṃvutassa, bhikkhave, viharato cittaṃ na byāsiñcati … pe … "
msgstr "When you live with the ear … nose … tongue … body … "

msgctxt "sn35.97:2.11"
msgid "appamādavihārītveva saṅkhaṃ gacchati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.97:2.12"
msgid "Manindriyaṃ saṃvutassa, bhikkhave, viharato cittaṃ na byāsiñcati, manoviññeyyesu dhammesu, "
msgstr "mind faculty restrained, your mind doesn’t become polluted when it comes to thoughts known by the mind. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:2.13"
msgid "tassa abyāsittacittassa pāmojjaṃ jāyati. "
msgstr "When the mind isn’t polluted, joy springs up. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:2.14"
msgid "Pamuditassa pīti jāyati. "
msgstr "Being joyful, rapture springs up. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:2.15"
msgid "Pītimanassa kāyo passambhati. "
msgstr "When the mind is full of rapture, the body becomes tranquil. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:2.16"
msgid "Passaddhakāyo sukhaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "When the body is tranquil, one feels bliss. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:2.17"
msgid "Sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati. "
msgstr "And when blissful, the mind becomes immersed in samādhi. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:2.18"
msgid "Samāhite citte dhammā pātubhavanti. "
msgstr "When the mind is immersed in samādhi, principles become clear. "

msgctxt "sn35.97:2.19"
msgid "Dhammānaṃ pātubhāvā appamādavihārītveva saṅkhaṃ gacchati. "
msgstr "Because principles have become clear, you’re considered to live diligently. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.97:2.20"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, appamādavihārī hotī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how someone lives diligently.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.97:2.21"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

